core.tut.pori.http

Class ResponseData

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.ResponseData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractTaskDetails, AutoCompleteResult, BackendDetails, Example, Example, Example, Example, Example, Example, Example, ExternalAccountConnectionList, FacebookProfile, FileList, JSONResponseData, MediaList, MediaObjectList, PhotoList, PicasaAlbumList, TaskResponse, TwitterProfile, UserCore.Registration, UserIdentityList, VideoList, WeightModifierList

    public abstract class ResponseData
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class for HTTP Response data. Sub-classes of this class can be used in combination with HTTP Response to provide automatic marshalling of object content to XML output. Note: implemented as abstract class because JAXB does not handle interfaces well.
